{
  "stem": "17761.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And now when I participated at the inauguration of the-- dedication of the Sefer Torah in Mamaroneck, State of New York, so I told again the story of that Torah.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What happened next, I think it was about a day after Simchat Torah, we were brought by the Romanian soldiers to the Dniester, put into little boats.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think they were made of gummy, of rubber, but I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were afraid that we would be just-- we heard stories about people not reaching the other side of the shore.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we came on the other side of the shore to a place that we didn't even know about its existence before called Mogilev-Podol'skii.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There all-- a lot of people came from all sides.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were brought there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the policy of the Romanian authorities at that time was to continue to chase the Jews in the other places of that big-- vast area called Transnistria.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were chased to [NON-ENGLISH], [NON-ENGLISH], [NON-ENGLISH], all kind of names that I forgot already.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And each group, people tried to get together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They bribed a lot of Romanian soldiers so they should go together either with their families or friends.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so there were little ghettos in all kinds of places in Transnistria.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My father wanted to remain in Mogilev.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Our idea was always the closer we are still back home, the more chances we have to get back home.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then it was also because the-- the-- there was many people there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we wanted to be in a big Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We felt somehow more secure.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was, as we say it, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You should know how to-- to manage the situation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Exactly how it happened, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
